*******Inheritance *****

### one class acquire properties of another class is inheritance

###Advantages 
         1. re-usability
         2. Extensibility
        
        ### Types of inheritance ###
        
        1.  Single Inheritance :
                             one class inherit from another parent class 
                             
        2.  Multi-Level Inheritance :
                               one class inherit from another  class and  another class also inherit from base/parent Class.
        3.  Hierarchical Inheritance :
                                one or more classes inherit from same base class is Hierarchical inheritance.
                                
                                
                                
                                
       ******/  Multiple Inheritance is not in Java :
                                              But it can be possible using interfaces in java.                                                                  



       









